title: LF Supp for duo plat 3+
body: D1 ADC last season, went overseas for like 4 months and now I seem to have lost my touch. Anyway im looking to climb up to dia again but I'm getting sick of soloq supps who don't know how to help me last hit under tower or just do the basics. I play from like 4-10:30pm AEST most days. hit me up :)
